      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem! It\u2019s in such incredible shape that it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014it\u2019s spotless inside and out, drives like a dream, and has been kept tucked away in a garage. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for its next adventure, this is the one! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
