    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a collector-grade E46 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated precision. At its heart lies the S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system that provides linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. This example features a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec 3.62 M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally flawless, with documented rear subframe reinforcement and recent valve clearance adjustments. Finished in concours-level Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the vehicle retains its original factory cross-hatch honing marks on the cylinders and shows zero bolster wear. This is a mechanically synchronized, turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
