    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing flawless original paintwork with a deep, mirror-like finish and an interior that still retains its factory-fresh aroma. Every surface, from the supple, uncreased leather upholstery to the high-gloss trim, is in showroom state. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule with every service documented. Equipped with premium features including a high-fidelity surround sound system, advanced driver assistance, and pristine alloy wheels wrapped in brand-new performance tires. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
